Using React, create a simple counter component that increments and decrements a count when clicking on respective buttons. 
Your task is to set up the component, manage the state, and ensure that the count is displayed on the screen

#ADDITONAL TASK 1
Additionally, implent the functionality so that the count cannot go below zero. 

#ADDITIONAL TASK 2 
Additionally, implement the functionality so that whenever user hover over button it increment/decrement 
